Package com.unvired.lib.utility

  • Interface Summary

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AttachmentInternal  
    Base64
    Base64 is a utility class with 2 simple functions Convert a stream of bytes to a Base64 string Decode a Base64 string into a byte stream .
    BusinessEntity
    BusinessEntity is a utility class that provides an object oriented view of any Business Object (Sales Order, Invoice, Business Partner etc) It is based on the premise that every entity in this world can be represented in a simple hierarchical relationship consisting of a single header and related items.
    IBXMLConstants
    The Class IBXMLConstants.
    InfoMessage
    InfoMessage is utility class used to construct information/error messages for propagation from the server to the client.
    JSONHandler  
    ProcessAgentUtility
    ProcessAgentUtility is a utility class for use by process agents to perform commonly used functions.
    Server
    The Class Server.
    Structure
    Structure is a utility class that is used to describe the properties of a Header or Item in a Business Entity.
    SystemMessage  
    XMLBuilder
    XMLBuilder is an utility class that provides a quick and easy alternative to constructing an XML Document.
    XMLHandler
    XMLHandler is an utility class that is used to extract (@link BusinessEntity} objects from an IBXML format and vice-versa.
